<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Thank you for your comment!</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
        }
        .container {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .feedback {
            width: 500px;
            height: 500px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            padding: 20px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .feedback img {
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
        }
        .feedback h1 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin: 0;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .feedback p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin: 0;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="feedback">
            <img src="/images/checkmark.svg" alt="checkmark">
            <h1>Thank you for your comment!</h1>
            <p>
                We appreciate that you took the time to submit a comment.
                Your comment will be reviewed and considered for future episodes!
            </p>
            <p>You can close this window now.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</html>
